315
00:11:26,100 --> 00:11:27,050
This Divine Healer

316
00:11:27,050 --> 00:11:28,570
is really a problem.

317
00:11:28,980 --> 00:11:30,050
She isn't supposed to be here,

318
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:32,860
