391
00:14:08,050 --> 00:14:10,050
You can let one person stay, Your Highness.

392
00:14:21,530 --> 00:14:22,770
Can you see some light?

393
00:14:23,220 --> 00:14:23,740
Yes.

394
00:14:30,140 --> 00:14:30,690
How about now?

395
00:14:38,940 --> 00:14:40,300
