873
00:33:20,530 --> 00:33:22,820
Your palms sweat when you're nervous.

874
00:33:23,210 --> 00:33:23,940
Don't worry.

875
00:33:26,970 --> 00:33:27,490
Zang Ming,

876
00:33:28,290 --> 00:33:30,250
