992
00:39:06,580 --> 00:39:07,220
You are here.

993
00:39:12,220 --> 00:39:14,430
It's a clear night to kill.

994
00:39:15,020 --> 00:39:16,220
Are you here

995
00:39:16,500 --> 00:39:17,950
