1018
00:40:21,950 --> 00:40:24,060
The Leader of Dark River is very powerful.

1019
00:40:25,310 --> 00:40:27,390
Are you confident that you will win?

1020
00:40:28,500 --> 00:40:29,620
Do you have any idea

1021
00:40:29,950 --> 00:40:31,020
